        " أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِنَّ أَحَقَّ اَلشُّرُوطِ أَنْ يُوفَى بِهَا مَا اِسْتَحْلَلْتُمْ بِهِ اَلْفُرُوجَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4401 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"Indeed, the most deserving of conditions to be fulfilled are those by which you make lawful access to private parts.\""
        ]
